# Architecture — {{ repo_name }}

## Overview

This project follows the **AstroData Data Science Skeleton** structure, powered by **FastForge ⚡**.

## Components

| Layer           | Path                              | Role                                      |
|-----------------|-----------------------------------|-------------------------------------------|
| FastAPI         | `src/{{ package_name }}/api/`     | REST API with OpenAPI docs                |
| Streamlit       | `app/streamlit_app.py`            | Interactive data dashboard                |
| Core            | `src/{{ package_name }}/core/`    | Shared utilities, config, version         |
| Data            | `src/{{ package_name }}/data/`    | ETL / ingestion pipelines                 |
| Features        | `src/{{ package_name }}/features/`| Feature engineering                       |
| Models          | `src/{{ package_name }}/models/`  | Training and inference                    |
| Visualization   | `src/{{ package_name }}/visualization/` | Plotting helpers                    |
| Tests           | `tests/`                          | Unit & integration tests (pytest)         |

## Data Flow

```
raw/ → ETL (data/) → interim/ → features/ → processed/ → models/ → API / Streamlit
```

## CI/CD

Pre-configured for both **GitHub Actions** and **GitLab CI**.
